playstore_details.title: Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier
playstore_details.description:
Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier app allows you to adjust the sound effect levels, the target is listening better to your music.
Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier recognizes if you can increase the sound requirement of your android device to get more tips while listening to music.
The application includes features that include:
- The equalizer allows the sound to search for frequency.
- Bass boost is a sound effect for preparing or amplifying low-frequency sounds.
- Virtualization is a Sound effect for virtualizing audio channels. Let's enhance the stereo effect.
 
Enhance the sound quality of your android device with Bass Boost, Virtualizer and Equalizer. Make music and video sound like never before. Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier lets you adjust the sound effect levels so that you get the best result from your Music, Audio or Video coming out of your device.
Improve your phone or tablet's sound quality with the first true global Equalizer app and home-screen widget! Equalizer lets you adjust sound effect levels so that you get the best out of your Music or Audio coming out of your phone. Apply Equalizer Presets based on Music Genre, or quickly create your own custom preset with the 5 band Equalizer controller.
Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier lets you adjust the frequency envelope of the sound with bands to enjoy music. Adjust audio balance between channels and And for a perfect music listening experience, it will achieve smooth transitions between your tracks for you
Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier is a powerful yet easy Music Equalizer with Bass Booster, Volume Booster and 3D Virtualization effects that increases the volume of your Android phone or tablet devices, enhancing unprecedented audio options!
Professional audio, video decoding technology that allows high-quality music and video playback. In addition, the most Professional EQ helps you manually control your music playback volume, enhance your music, and increase your volume.
 
Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier makes it possible to mix, edit and adapt sounds on your tracks to provide optimum music listening. It adjusts the music with powerful equalizer and higher frequencies.
Trans Plays your playlist with special DJ transitions like a DJ, you can control the sound in accordance with the rhythm of the music alt you direct the sound!
 If you're an audio freak, you want more control over the equalizer. It is a new generation app that will extend your player's capabilities and will drastically improve the sound quality! Specifically designed for Android, Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier app will help you get the most out of your music!
 With the band equalizer, you have more control over tone and pitch. Play around with the bands, moving them up and down, and get a feel for the effect they make on the sound. A small adjustment can have a major impact.
Download Music Equalizer & Bass Booster & Volume Amplifier and listen to the music however you want, Enjoy it.
